Geometry equations:\Pdh = bottom_height + top_height = height - side_height - opening_height\Pdw = 0.5 * (bottom_width - top_width) \Pxb = bottom_height * tan(bottom_angle - PI/2)\Pxt = top_height * tan(top_angle - PI/2)\Pxt + side_height * tan(slot_
  3
angle / 2) = dw + xb\P\PSubstitute xt and xb:\Ptop_height * tan(top_angle - PI/2) + side_height * tan(slot_angle / 2) = dw + bottom_height * tan(bottom_angle - PI/2)\P\PResulting linear system:\Pbottom_height = dh - top_height\Ptop_height = (dw + bot
  3
tom_height * tan(bottom_angle - PI/2) - side_height * tan(slot_angle / 2)) / tan(top_angle - PI/2)\P\PSolving for bottom_height:\Pbottom_height (1 + tan(bottom_angle - PI/2)/tan(top_angle - PI/2)) = dh - (dw  - side_height * tan(slot_angle / 2)) / ta
  1
n(top_angle - PI/2)\Pbottom_height = (dh - (dw - side_height * tan(slot_angle / 2)) / tan(top_angle - PI/2)) / (1 + tan(bottom_angle - PI/2)/tan(top_angle - PI/2))\P\P
